  "slug": "joy-adv-central-tech-university",
  "status": "publish",
  "type": "page",
  "link": "https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/success\/joy-adv-central-tech-university\/",
  "title": { "rendered": "Joy adv. Central Tech University" },
  "content": {
    "rendered": "<div id=\"pl-290\" class=\"panel-layout\">\n<div id=\"pg-290-0\" class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\">\n<div id=\"pgc-290-0-0\" class=\"panel-grid-cell\" data-weight=\"1\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"pg-290-1\" class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_repeat&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;no_margin&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\">\n<div id=\"pgc-290-1-0\" class=\"panel-grid-cell\" data-weight=\"0.5\">\n<div id=\"panel-290-1-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"1\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\">\n<div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\">\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/02\/City.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-988 alignright\" src=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/02\/City.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"432\" height=\"270\" srcset=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/02\/City.jpg 450w, https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/02\/City-300x187.jpg 300w, https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/02\/City-436x272.jpg 436w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 432px) 100vw, 432px\" \/><\/a>Plaintiffs brought a lawsuit against my client for breach of contract and fraud involving a production contract for three concerts to be performed at The Sports Arena. The plaintiffs claimed they sustained $500,000 in damages.<\/p>\n<p>My client cross-complained against plaintiffs for breach of contract, fraud and common counts for money due and owing to our client pursuant to their written contract. I obtained a defense verdict for our client and the plaintiffs took nothing on their complaint. \u00a0I also recovered $10,000 in costs against the plaintiffs.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"pgc-290-1-1\" class=\"panel-grid-cell\" data-weight=\"0.5\">\n<div id=\"panel-290-1-1-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-image panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"2\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n",
    "protected": false
  },
  "excerpt": {
    "rendered": "<p>Plaintiffs brought a lawsuit against my client for breach of contract and fraud involving a production contract for three concerts to be performed at The Sports Arena. The plaintiffs claimed they sustained $500,000 in damages. My client cross-complained against plaintiffs for breach of contract, fraud and common counts for money due and owing to our client pursuant to their written contract. I obtained a defense verdict for our client and the plaintiffs took nothing on their complaint. \u00a0I also recovered $10,000 in costs against the plaintiffs.<\/p>\n",
    "protected": false
  },
